{"tid":610818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京賞櫻季節中國觀光客湧入 打架、噪音樣樣來","createTime":"2018-03-30T10:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T15:46:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"166f79c9982c9aab20680d862ecbb67b49c29946","tid":610818,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phphrZORb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phphrZORb.jpg&h=185f8bae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本東京都台東區上野恩賜公園近來櫻花綻放，許多日本民眾利用閒暇之餘到此處遊憩、賞櫻，卻有中國遊客自備座席佔位，還拿出預藏的南胡樂器與友人大唱京劇橋段自得其樂，讓當地人難忍噪音，甚至還有中國遊客與他國遊客在櫻花樹下當眾打群架。<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日放送》專題節目引述中國政府統計數據表示，2018年到日本賞櫻花的中國遊客比去年還要多出60%，節目製作人員實地走訪東京上野恩賜公園，發現中國遊客賞櫻的言行舉止水準欠佳，干擾其他遊客，也嚴重影響週邊環境安寧，甚至在當地晚間9點過後，還有中國遊客吹奏樂器、玩撲克牌，無視園內禁止事項規定。<br />\n<br />\n日本媒體在晚間12點過後，親眼目擊中國遊客因佔位問題，與孟加拉遊客以簡單的日文發生爭執，一言不合大打出手，被當地公園管理處人員制止，甚至有中國遊客不諳日本法規，向管理員提出在公園久待的合法性，但被管理員搬出公園管理規定打臉，日本民眾們都對此感到相當無奈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpfeGliv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpfeGliv.jpg&h=0fa4d3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n節目製作人員實地走訪東京上野恩賜公園，發現中國遊客水準欠教育，嚴重影響週邊環境安寧。（圖擷取自朝日放送）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpLHTnBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpLHTnBg.jpg&h=834f7b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上野公園禁止演奏樂器，但中國遊客沒在怕。（圖擷取自朝日放送）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jyyFslk2VmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjyyFslk2VmQ&d=%2Fw6tNE5AmV4a9nGMYKjewaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=3a221e46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jyyFslk2VmQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ykE-O1vSegI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DykE-O1vSegI&d=%2Fw6tNE5AmV4a9nGMYKjewaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=9f1b1460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ykE-O1vSegI</a>"},{"pid":"7d3938c6aae90ae5425c5dc119837bbc91787599","tid":610818,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:04:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2379721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2379721&d=%2Fw6tNE5AmV4a9nGMYKjewaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=b7d6c04f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2379721&h=f32746d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2379721</a>"},{"pid":"110ddfd4190b8fafa915d5e3918228e3e4b285a5","tid":610818,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"遲下會有假乞兒添"},{"pid":"2a118d2e3eac0e57e74cfeecc81710746d7ea446","tid":610818,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"抵制呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d22db775518e06d7ee326e5db1364a9d5b9427","tid":610818,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"支那狗人見人憎好正常"},{"pid":"ea1ebeb17c8c6731293dcd48f58955432db82b96","tid":610818,"uid":130897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d37b184b4a1670534070f1e16222b33d0dcda2","tid":610818,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"二胡真係難聽到仆街"},{"pid":"e3941fc6c829f9846c1b7fff572aa0753d75225b","tid":610818,"uid":179467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score